        "key": "CovenantData_descriptionKey-8d23a83af7eaaccb-f7009ac0327c41e42836e43c3798df0e-v2",
        "english": "Bosses have increased [attack] and [health]. Non-Flying Bosses have an additional mechanic.",
        "french": "[attack] et [health] des boss augmentés. Les boss non volants ont une mécanique supplémentaire.",
        "german": "Bosse verfügen über mehr [attack] und [health]. Nicht-fliegende Bosse verfügen über einen zusätzlichen Mechanismus.",
        "russian": "У боссов повышены [attack] и [health]. У нелетающих боссов есть дополнительная механика.",
        "portuguese": "Os Chefões têm um aumento de [attack] e [health]. Os Chefões que não são Voadores têm uma mecânica adicional.",
        "chinese": "首领拥有更多 [attack] 和 [health]。非飞行首领拥有一项额外机制。",
        "spanish": "Los jefes tienen más [attack] y [health]. Los jefes que no vuelan tienen una mecánica adicional.",
        "chinese_traditional": "首領擁有更高的[attack]和[health]。非飛行首領擁有額外機制。",
        "korean": "보스의 [attack] 및 [health]이 증가합니다. 비행하지 않는 보스에게는 새로운 메커니즘이 추가됩니다.",
        "japanese": "ボスの[attack]と[health]が増加する。非飛行型のボスにギミックが追加される。"
      },
